  "industry_note": "Victrex 450G — Victrex 의 baseline unfilled PEEK granule (medium MFR for injection molding). Tg 143°C, Tm 343°C, max service 250°C continuous, 315°C short-term. σy 100 / UTS 100 / El 30-50% / E 3.7 GPa / ρ 1.30 g/cc. UL 94 V-0 자체 난연 (limiting oxygen index 35%). 가공 시 ~370°C 압출, 결정화 후 dimensional 안정. 의료 임플란트 (ASTM F2026 spinal cage), 산업 기어/베어링, 반도체 wafer carrier, 오일 well-head seal."
